# Anna and Sarah discover that a tiny spider can be surprising and helpful.

title: Anna, Sarah & the Tiny Spider
scene: park

ANNA walks in from left
ANNA (happy): What a beautiful day for a picnic!
ANNA sits

SARAH runs in from right
SARAH (scared): Anna! There is a spider beside you!
ANNA trembles
ANNA (surprised): Oh! It is very tiny.

SARAH trembles
ANNA nods
ANNA: Let's watch it from here.

camera zooms on ANNA
ANNA (happy): Look, Sarah. It is making a sparkly web.
camera resets

SARAH points
SARAH (surprised): It caught the mosquito that was buzzing around us!
ANNA laughs
SARAH laughs

SARAH (happy): Thank you, little spider!
ANNA stands
ANNA waves
SARAH waves
ANNA (happy): Every tiny creature has an important job.
